sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeRouter as KServe Router<br/>Gateway API
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OpenAI as vLLM OpenAI API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vLLM TGIS Adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.x+
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3 / HF Hub)

    Note over Engine,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading (startup)
    Engine->>Storage: Download/mount model weights<br/>HTTPS 443 (TLS 1.2+) or filesystem
    Storage-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>GPU: Load model to VRAM<br/>CUDA API
    GPU-->>Engine: Model ready

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: OpenAI API Inference Request
    Client->>KServeRouter: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS 443 (TLS 1.2+)
    KServeRouter->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS 8443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Bearer Token (JWT)
    KRBP->>KRBP: Validate JWT against<br/>Kubernetes RBAC
    KRBP->>OpenAI: Forward (pre-authenticated)<br/>HTTP 8000 (plaintext localhost)
    OpenAI->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>GPU: Execute model forward pass<br/>CUDA API
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result (tokens)
    Engine-->>OpenAI: Generated text
    OpenAI-->>KRBP: JSON response
    KRBP-->>KServeRouter: HTTPS response
    KServeRouter-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>KServeRouter: gRPC GenerationService.Generate<br/>HTTPS 443 (TLS 1.2+)
    KServeRouter->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS 8443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Bearer Token (JWT)
    KRBP->>KRBP: Validate JWT against<br/>Kubernetes RBAC
    KRBP->>TGIS: Forward (pre-authenticated)<br/>gRPC 8033 (plaintext localhost)
    TGIS->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>GPU: Execute model forward pass<br/>CUDA API
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result (tokens)
    Engine-->>TGIS: Generated text
    TGIS-->>KRBP: gRPC response
    KRBP-->>KServeRouter: HTTPS response
    KServeRouter-->>Client: gRPC response
